Description: keyboard-first i3/X11 desktop configuration layer
 STACKI3-Space packages an i3, Polybar, Rofi, Dunst, tmux and shell
 workflow for Linux Mint and other Debian-like X11 desktops.
 .
 This package installs the STACKI3-Space payload under
 /usr/share/stacki3-space and provides the stacki3-space command. User
 configuration is applied explicitly with stacki3-space apply, so apt
 upgrades do not overwrite files in $HOME automatically.
